Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.53,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:50.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Let's Talk\N with Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.84,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Talk with Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:22:58.69,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a chat, Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:04.05,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any hobbies \Nbesides sleeping, Dorothy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.05,0:23:06.22,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, let me guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:09.05,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Maybe dancin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:09.92,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,...ggh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:12.10,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe even cookin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:13.40,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,...ggh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:15.69,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you cook a great hambur...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:16.65,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,...gghr.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:19.08,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,And I bet dessert is caramel puddin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:20.12,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,...ggh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:23.34,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to eat your \Ncooking one day, Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:27.10,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's battle, and if \NI win, you'll cook me a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:31.31,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Rock, paper... paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:42.65,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourselves members \Nof the glorious Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.34,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.44,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we'll go into the hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:49.94,main,mere,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 72: "Saint Elmo's Fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 72\N\N{\fs18} Saint Elmo's Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:53.74,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Being naked with others... \NThat's my magic!
